cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this benchmark, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "A Harmonised Open Panel Benchmark for Causal, Fairness-Aware,
  and Explainable Machine Learning in Educational Equity and SDG 4 Monitoring"
authors:
