repository-code: "https://github.com/your-org/ukci2026-education-equity-benchmark"
license: MIT
date-released: "2026-06-01"
version: "1.0.0"
abstract: >
  A reproducible 12-country balanced panel dataset (2015–2024)
  integrating World Bank WDI/WGI and UNESCO UIS data across 17
  indicators, with a five-task benchmark suite (outcome prediction,
  trajectory classification, fairness-aware learning, MNAR imputation,
  causal ML) designed to support SDG 4 monitoring research in the
  computational intelligence community.
keywords:
  - educational equity
  - SDG 4
  - causal machine learning
  - algorithmic fairness
  - panel data
  - MNAR imputation
  - Double Machine Learning
  - trajectory classification
  - gender parity index
  - benchmark dataset
